                                <support>
                                    <p>Several fragments of a white <material>marble</material> <objectType>panel</objectType>: two adjoining fragments (a and c) found
                        and published together, fragment b published separately, but adjoining a on top; the panel was progressively thicker from upper left to lower right.
                                    Fragment a)
                                    <dimensions>
                                            <width>0.19</width>
                                            <height>0.22</height>
                                            <depth>0.035</depth>
                                    </dimensions>;
                                    fragment b) 
                                    <dimensions>
                                        <width>0.09</width>
                                        <height>0.07</height>
                                        <depth>0.04</depth>
                                    </dimensions>;
                                    fragment c)
                                    <dimensions>
                                        <width>0.155</width>
                                        <height>0.23</height>
                                        <depth>0.06</depth>
                                    </dimensions>.</p>
                                </support>
                            </supportDesc>
